text: Polyrhaphis batesi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Hovore and McCarty in 1998. It is known from El Salvador, Honduras, Guatemala, Costa Rica, Nicaragua, Mexico, and Panama.BioLib.cz - Polyrhaphis batesi.
